{
  "text": "30 female adult flies (0-1 day old) per sample were collected and Western blot analyses were performed as previously described [CITATION_1] . Primary antibodies used were anti-C-DmWWOX antibody (1:1000) (49) and mouse monoclonal anti-\u03b2-tubulin antibody (1:2000, Sigma). Secondary antibodies used were Anti-Rabbit DyLight 649 antibody (1:2500, Vector Laboratories) and anti-mouse-Cy3antibody (1:200, Jackson Laboratories).",
